{
  "_metadata": {
    "_comment": "theme-config.json ‚Äî Defines all visual themes for the app.",
    "_comment_2": "All colours are in hex format. Opacity variants use hex alpha prefix e.g. #1A4F46E5 = 10% opacity of #4F46E5.",
    "_comment_3": "All font sizes are BASE sizes for 'medium' text scale. The app multiplies these by the text_scale_factor.",
    "_comment_4": "text_scale_factors: small=0.85, medium=1.0, large=1.2. These are global multipliers applied to ALL font sizes.",
    "_comment_5": "Spacing and radius values are in logical pixels (dp/pt ‚Äî Flutter handles platform differences).",
    "_comment_6": "Animation settings here are defaults. Master on/off switch is in global-config.json under animations.enabled.",
    "_comment_7": "active_theme: set to the theme_id the app should load. Changed when user picks a theme.",
    "_comment_8": "Each theme has a light and dark variant. The app respects device dark mode unless user overrides in preferences.",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "last_updated": "2026-02-23",
    "config_owner": "design_system"
  },

  "active_theme": "midnight_focus",
